00:08:06.390 --> 00:08:09.130
Mental health court
has been developed

00:08:09.130 --> 00:08:15.310
to create a special procedure where
mentally ill offenders charged

00:08:15.310 --> 00:08:18.950
with criminal activities
will be diverted

00:08:18.950 --> 00:08:27.460
from correctional facilities to
community mental health based care.

00:08:29.240 --> 00:08:32.200
Yes, thank you.

00:08:33.540 --> 00:08:41.150 position:56%
The shared goal of the mental health
court are to improve public safety

00:08:41.150 --> 00:08:48.690
by reducing criticism, improving
the quality of life of people

00:08:48.690 --> 00:08:54.980
with mental illness by
increasing their participation

00:08:54.980 --> 00:08:59.800
in effective treatment,
and reducing court

00:08:59.800 --> 00:09:03.720
and correctional related costs.

00:09:03.720 --> 00:09:08.700
This philosophical point
of view is not new,

00:09:08.700 --> 00:09:15.890 position:56%
as it follows several approaches
including crisis intervention teams,

00:09:15.890 --> 00:09:21.810
jail diversion programs,
specialized probation

00:09:21.810 --> 00:09:24.240
and parole caseloads developed

00:09:24.240 --> 00:09:31.070
to address the significant
over-representation of people

00:09:31.070 --> 00:09:34.990
with mental illness in the
criminal justice system.

00:09:34.990 --> 00:09:43.990
The estimate brings the percentage
inmates with serious mental illness

00:09:43.990 --> 00:09:52.900
to 20%, therefore triggering a
reading of the c'est la vie gamble

00:09:52.900 --> 00:09:58.350
of 1976 where the supreme
court determined

00:09:58.350 --> 00:10:03.960 position:56%
that the 8th amendment requires that
prison officials provide a system

00:10:03.960 --> 00:10:12.400
of adequate medical care
including mental health care.

00:10:13.590 --> 00:10:16.580
&gt;&gt; In another approach
to address crime

00:10:16.580 --> 00:10:23.120
in the United States is worth
considering as the US continues

00:10:23.120 --> 00:10:31.270 position:56%
to highest incarceration rate in
the world with 5% of the population,

00:10:31.270 --> 00:10:35.170
but nearly 25% of the
