in schizophrenia, bipolar disorder,
major depression as well as anxiety.

00:21:38.290 --> 00:21:46.850
And it is important to make a
difference between this pathology

00:21:46.850 --> 00:21:53.920
and what was called axis two
pathology in the DSM full manual,

00:21:53.920 --> 00:21:58.930
which was referring to
personality disorders.

00:21:59.970 --> 00:22:10.740
The belief was that people this
major mental illness have less

00:22:10.740 --> 00:22:16.490
control, or even no control,
over their behavior and that

00:22:16.490 --> 00:22:22.110
in the position to the personality
disorder, patient [inaudible].

00:22:22.110 --> 00:22:27.230
But there are two remarks.

00:22:27.230 --> 00:22:33.730
The first one is that this
early distinction in control,

00:22:33.730 --> 00:22:37.700
or lack of such, depending
on the diagnosis given,

00:22:37.700 --> 00:22:44.120
this early distinction is now
challenged by recent findings

00:22:44.120 --> 00:22:52.100
where functional brain images are
showing some remarkable difference

00:22:52.100 --> 00:22:56.940
in the brain of the individual
suffering from personality disorder

00:22:56.940 --> 00:23:01.760
versus individuals
with no mental illness.

00:23:01.760 --> 00:23:04.010
So in light of such findings,

00:23:04.010 --> 00:23:08.040
the question of whether
those individuals

00:23:08.040 --> 00:23:12.040
with personality disorders
have control

00:23:12.040 --> 00:23:18.170
over their behavior provides
more and more cloudy answers,

00:23:18.170 --> 00:23:26.910
because the more scientific medical
data obtained shows the abnormality

00:23:26.910 --> 00:23:29.910
of the brain function.

00:23:29.910 --> 00:23:33.400
Another element which
is worth mentioning is

00:23:33.400 --> 00:23:39.590
that this very practical DSM
full classification of axis one

00:23:39.590 --> 00:23:50.690 position:56%
and axis two of personality disorder
is not removed because a new DSM,

00:23:50.690 --> 00:23:55.370
which stands for diagnostic
and statistical manual

00:23:55.370 --> 00:23:59.190
of mental disorder, this new
classification does not have those

00:23:59.190 --> 00:24:03.660
axis anymore, so the
realm of mental illness

00:24:03.660 --> 00:24:07.220
